description: This dataset shows, as of September 2014, the anticipated average number of plan reviews, broken out by county, for projects approved by the State Highway Administration's (SHA's) Access Management Division (AMD). SHA plans to begin tracking the actual average plan review cycles. These data are an estimate only of what the collected data will show.
